    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const reminders = [\n  \"Hey there, Planeswalker! Just a friendly reminder: for new card requests, please use the `/request-list` command. This helps us keep everything organized and get your cards to you faster!\",\n  \"Got a new card you need for your deck? Don't forget to use `/request-list` to submit your new requests. It's the best way to make sure your wish list gets to our team.\",\n  \"Quick tip for your next request: use the `/request-list` command! This keeps all your single card requests in one clean list, making it easier for us to track them down for you.\",\n  \"Before you cast that next spell... remember to use `/request-list` for all new card requests. Using the command ensures your request is officially logged with the store!\",\n  \"Time to add some new cards to your collection? For all new singles requests, please remember to use `/request-list` to submit them. Happy deck building!\"\n];\n\nconst randomIndex = Math.floor(Math.random() * reminders.length);\nconst randomMessage = reminders[randomIndex];\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    message: randomMessage\n  }\n}];"
      },
